metadata.name: ARCTIC DREAMSCAPE #1/10
metadata.description:
'ARCTIC DREAMSCAPE' is the genesis drop of FRVNK. The photo was taken at sunset during an expedition in the Svalbard Arctic, capturing a dreamy and ethereal landscape of ice and snow. It also showcases the rugged, untouched wilderness of one of the world's most remote regions.

by FRVNK / Frank Liu

---
